---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Collaborative Frontend Engineering" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    With a strong understanding of <span class="text-primary"
      >design principles</span
    > and
    <span class="text-primary">user experience</span>, I strive to build
    applications that are <span class="text-primary"
      >performant, accessible, and user-friendly</span
    >.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/HeumannMarkus_CV_en.pdf"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="telescope" class="h-8" />
      <span>Read the resume</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="mailto:hey@mrks.me"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="email" class="h-8" />
      <span>Contact me</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
